UID:occ-2578@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Cabaret
DESCRIPTION:Divas\, Drama & Bad Decisions: a small-room song set from thre
 e Out of Box audience favorites\, directed by Annie Cook.\n\nA cabaret tit
 led Divas\, Drama & Bad Decisions\, sung close-up in Out of Box Theatre's 
 black box as part of its Creator's Den program. Annie Cook directs a trio 
 of regulars from the company's stages: Emily Kalat\, Emily Sams Brown\, an
 d MK Penley.
