BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Comedy Class Showcase
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260816T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260816T203000
DTSTAMP:20260716T154725Z
UID:occ-1769@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Stand-up Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Graduates of Out of Box Theatre's first stand-up class perform
  the sets they built over eight weeks.\n\nThe debut of Out of Box Theatre'
 s first Stand-Up Comedy Class: after eight weeks of writing and workshoppi
 ng\, the students step up to the mic to deliver the material they built\, 
 one night only. New comics\, fresh jokes\, and a room ready to root for th
 em.
GEO:33.9148699;-84.3601692
LAST-MODIFIED:20260716T154716Z
LOCATION:Out of Box Theatre\, 585 Cobb Pkwy SE\, Suite G-1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/ticketing/comedy-at-the-den-class-showcase
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Comedy at the Den
