DTSTAMP:20260716T154725Z
UID:occ-1185@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:3
CATEGORIES:Stand-up Comedy
DESCRIPTION:A stand-up showcase in a deliberately small room\, hosted by A
 tlanta comedian Jessica "It's All Good."\n\nA lineup of stand-up comics wi
 th distinct styles\, hosted by Atlanta comedian Jessica "It's All Good\," 
 known for sharp observations and a warm hand on the mic. The room is inten
 tionally small\, with limited seats and almost no distance between you and
  the performers. Presented by Out of Box Theatre.
